OL,3,CCastle Water vows to create 2,000 jobs
OL,4,Cat Thames Water in fresh bid approach
OL,6,FCastle Water has vowed to create up to
OL,7,F2,000 jobs at Thames Water if it gains
OL,8,Fcontrol of the struggling supplier, as
OL,9,Fpart of a fresh approach that also
OL,10,Foffers an extra #1 billion cash
OL,11,Finjection above current proposals.
OL,13,FThe utility firm has returned with an
OL,14,Fimproved proposal for Thames, which is
OL,15,Fin advanced talks with creditors and
OL,16,Fregulators to secure funding that
OL,17,Fwould stave off nationalisation.
OL,19,FCastle Water was one of the companies
OL,20,Fthat had approached Thames about a
OL,21,Fpossible deal earlier this year.
