OL,3,CCastle Water vows to create 2,000 jobs
OL,4,Cat Thames Water in fresh bid approach
OL,6,FIts initial bid was rejected in favour
OL,7,Fof proposals by investment group KKR,
OL,8,Fwhich later pulled out of the bidding.
OL,10,FThames is currently in talks with a
OL,11,Fconsortium of its main creditors,
OL,12,Fnamed London & Valley Water, which has
OL,13,Fsubmitted plans to pump investment
OL,14,Finto the utility and write off debts
OL,15,Fin return for more lenient performance
OL,16,Ftargets.
