OL,3,CCastle Water vows to create 2,000 jobs
OL,4,Cat Thames Water in fresh bid approach
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Castle Water says its
OL,7,Falternative plans would offer a cash
OL,8,Finjection of at least #1 billion above
OL,9,Fthe current proposals, backed by the
OL,10,Fproperty group of the billionaire
OL,11,FPears family.
OL,13,FIf a bid were successful, it would
OL,14,Falso create up to 2,000 jobs as part
OL,15,Fof a 25% increase in spending,
OL,16,Fincluding engineers, scientists and
OL,17,Foperational staff, the PA news agency
OL,18,Funderstands.
