OL,3,CCastle Water vows to create 2,000 jobs
OL,4,Cat Thames Water in fresh bid approach
OL,6,FThe sweetened offering also includes
OL,7,Fcommitments to repair and expand
OL,8,Fcapacity in waste treatment plants to
OL,9,Freduce pollution.
OL,11,FCastle Water is co-owned by
OL,12,FConservative Party treasurer Graham
OL,13,FEdwards and says it is the largest
OL,14,Findependent water retailer in the UK.
OL,16,FIts chief John Reynolds said in an
OL,17,Finterview with The Times that he was
OL,18,F"confident" the turnaround plan would
OL,19,Fsolve pollution problems at Thames.
