OL,3,CCastle Water vows to create 2,000 jobs
OL,4,Cat Thames Water in fresh bid approach
OL,6,FHe also said he believes discussions
OL,7,Fbetween Thames and its creditors and
OL,8,Finvestors had stalled due to the
OL,9,Fnature of its proposals.
OL,11,FHowever, a spokesman for the creditors
OL,12,Fsaid it was "simply not true that
OL,13,Fdiscussions have stalled".
OL,15,F"Thames Water needs #5 billion of
OL,16,Furgent funding from committed and
OL,17,Fexperienced new investors to deliver
OL,18,Fimproved outcomes for its customers
OL,19,Fand employees," London & Valley Water
OL,20,Fsaid.
