OL,3,CCastle Water vows to create 2,000 jobs
OL,4,Cat Thames Water in fresh bid approach
OL,6,F"We are working hard to secure a
OL,7,Fsolution as quickly as possible."
OL,9,FIt is understood that discussions had
OL,10,Fslowed in the lead-up to the autumn
OL,11,FBudget on November 26, after which
OL,12,Ftalks with the Treasury over the
OL,13,Fproposals are expected to accelerate.
OL,15,FThe consortium is hoping to finalise a
OL,16,Frescue deal before Christmas.
OL,18,FIt has vowed to write off around #4
OL,19,Fbillion, or 25% of the debt it holds
OL,20,Fin Thames, plus debt held by other
OL,21,Fcreditors.
