OL,3,CCastle Water vows to create 2,000 jobs
OL,4,Cat Thames Water in fresh bid approach
OL,6,FIncluding an extra #150 million of new
OL,7,Fequity, the lenders said they are
OL,8,Fpumping in a further #1 billion of
OL,9,Finvestment, on top of the proposal
OL,10,Fsubmitted to regulator Ofwat in May.
OL,12,FHowever, the proposal comes with an
OL,13,Feffective ultimatum to Ofwat for it to
OL,14,Faccept renegotiated targets on
OL,15,Fpollution incidents and water leaks in
OL,16,Freturn for the investment.
OL,18,FA spokesman for Thames said that
OL,19,Fdiscussions were ongoing.
